---
title: Crumbed Chicken & Bacon Caesar Salad with Croutons & Parmesan Cheese
description: Short on time but need a salad dressed to impress, then you really can’t compete with a caesar-style salad. This one has golden
crumbed chicken strips to go with a delicious dijon aioli dressing. This salad is ready to be centre of attention.
